%pyspark

from urllib2 import urlopen
import pandas as pd
import re, os

def airbnburlminer(country='singapore', dataset='listings', ext='.csv.gz'):
    page = urlopen('http://insideairbnb.com/get-the-data.html')
    html = page.read().decode("utf-8")
    urlarr = [str(re.sub('<a href=".*?', "", csvfile)).replace('"','') for csvfile in re.findall('<a href=".*{}.*?{}{}"'.format(country,dataset,ext), html)]
    print('\n'.join(urlarr))
    return pd.concat(map(lambda file: pd.read_csv(file, low_memory=False), urlarr))
    

df = airbnburlminer()
df = df.drop_duplicates()
